query:
SELECT
                r.id,
                c.name,
                r.version as "version: Version",
                r.release_time
            FROM
                crates AS c
                INNER JOIN releases AS r ON r.crate_id = c.id
            WHERE
                r.archive_storage IS TRUE AND
                r.id >= $1 AND
                r.id <= $2
            ORDER BY
                r.id DESC
